e i, a_{i, j} 
e a_{i, l}$$$ for $$$j 
e l$$$) follow — the chapters required to understand the $$$i$$$-th chapter. It is guaranteed that the sum of $$$n$$$ and sum of $$$k_i$$$ over all testcases do not exceed $$$2\cdot10^5$$$.
